children.name: Rules
children.text:
Setup:
- Give characters in secret to players(p):
4p: 2{lightning}2{mystic} - 5p: 2{lightning}2{mystic}1{water} - 6p: 2{lightning}2{mystic}2{water}
7p: 2{lightning}2{mystic}3{water} - 8p: 3{lightning}3{mystic}2{water}
- Randomize locations in pairs
- Each p chooses  color and goes to NoDamage

Turn:
- Move. Use D4+D6. Go to location of number. 7 you chose where. Cannot repeat area.
-  (optional) Do the action on the Location
-  (optional) Attack. Choose target, has to be in your location or adjacent. Do abs(D6-D4) damage.

Rules:
- If you kill a char, you get 1 equipment
- When dead, reveal
- If win condition is met, reveal and end the game. Can be multiple winners
